# Project Brief

- This is the ASra React + Vite site with routes: `/`, `/about`, `/founder-story`, `/record-of-soul`, `/spirit-medicine`, `/universal-matrix`, `/our-achievements`.
- Build before finishing substantive changes: `npm run build`.

# Copy Source Of Truth

- For rendered English and Chinese page copy, the source of truth is `docs/page-copy/*.xlsx`.
- After workbook edits, run `npm run copy:import`.
- This generates `src/content/pageCopyDocs.generated.ts`.
- The app reads workbook text through `src/content/pageCopyRuntime.ts`.
- Do not hand-edit `src/content/pageCopyDocs.generated.ts`.
- For detailed rules see `.cursor/rules/content-sync.mdc`.

# Main Edit Points

- UI strings: `src/i18n/messages/*.ts`
- Workbook runtime mapping: `src/content/pageCopyRuntime.ts`
- Structural fallback content: `src/content/siteContent.ts`, `src/content/founderStory2026Content.ts`
- Spirit Medicine structural data: `src/content/spiritMedicineData.ts`, `src/content/spiritMedicineOfficialOutline.ts`
- Universal Matrix structure: `src/content/universalMatrixSeries.ts`
- Achievements assets: `src/content/achievements2025Content.ts`

# Rules

- Prefer updating workbook-driven content at the workbook source, not by patching rendered text in multiple places.
- If duplicate `block_key` appears in multiple workbooks, the first workbook by filename wins.
- Treat `AGENTS.md` and `README.md` as supporting docs; this rule is the shortest current briefing.
